nodes.title: About me
nodes.info: As a mobile application developer, Ozan is mainly worked for small- to large-sized companies in the technology sector.  Ozan studied Computer Engineering at Ege University. Ozan believes that stay up to date in the workplace is the key to success⁠—a concept he lives out through his interests in table tennis, tennis, exercise, walking and discovering new places. Ozan enjoys meeting new people and learning about their lives and backgrounds. He easily finds common interests with strangers and tends to make most people feel comfortable.  He finds this skill  especially advantageous, when working in a team.
